==========
 REGISTER 
==========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license:  this file is in the public domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

allow registering of anon users

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *register-enable*

    :description: enable register command

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !register-enable
        <output> register enabled


2) *register*

    :description: register yourself to the bot .. this only works in jabber

    :permissions: ANY

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !register dunker
        <output> we already have a user with userhost test@test


3) *register-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !register-cfg
        <output> options: enable=1 .. perms=['USER'] .. version="GOZERBOT
        <output>  0.9"


4) *register-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !register-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


5) *register-disable*

    :description: disable register command

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !register-disable
        <output> register disabled


